    {
      "id": "PopularPost208966",
      "post_content": "[Blasphemous Act](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blasphemous Act), [Greater Gargadon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Greater Gargadon), and [Chancellor of the Forge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chancellor of the Forge) all work \\*really\\* well with this (because they're usable whether this is in hand or not.)   \n  \nAlso, consider using it next to something like [Boom](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boom)//Bust, where one half of the card is playable early game if you need it, but the other half has a big CMC. This counts \\*total\\* CMC btw, which means you actually get +8 for that card. Same with [Rough](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rough)//Tumble. [Slice and Dice](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slice and Dice) fits here as well.  \n  \nEverything here is 2 mana or less to use but give between +7 and +10; making the deck easy to assemble and use even with, say, 18 lands. ",
      "posted_by": "blurrymadness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost208966\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blasphemous Act\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blasphemous Act\">Blasphemous Act</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Greater Gargadon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Greater Gargadon\">Greater Gargadon</a>, and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chancellor of the Forge\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chancellor of the Forge\">Chancellor of the Forge</a> all work *really* well with this (because they're usable whether this is in hand or not.) <br/><br/>Also, consider using it next to something like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Boom\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Boom\">Boom</a>//Bust, where one half of the card is playable early game if you need it, but the other half has a big CMC. This counts *total* CMC btw, which means you actually get +8 for that card. Same with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rough\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rough\">Rough</a>//Tumble. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Slice and Dice\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slice and Dice\">Slice and Dice</a> fits here as well.<br/><br/>Everything here is 2 mana or less to use but give between +7 and +10; making the deck easy to assemble and use even with, say, 18 lands. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '208966'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44651\">blurrymadness</span>\r\n                                (7/15/2013 1:51:24 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
