    {
      "id": "PopularPost362747",
      "post_content": "@Fictionarius: Contrary to what you think, it's pretty obvious [Dark Depths](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Depths) is the problematic one. That's why it is the one banned in Modern, not [Vampire Hexmage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vampire Hexmage). A card like Dark Depths could either see no play at all or be a part of a broken combo, there is no middle ground. The Hexmage is a much more reasonable card; as if this even needs to be said.  \n  \nAs for infect, I think they made the mistake of not costing it as if it was double strike, because in decks that try to kill as fast as possible, it is basically double strike. [Fencing Ace](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fencing Ace) is a 1-power double strike that costs two. That's why [Glistener Elf](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glistener Elf) should not have costed one, and [Blighted Agent](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blighted Agent) probably should have been somewhat less powerful at two, if not gotten moved to three. 1/1 double strike for one is just not fair.",
      "posted_by": "sweetgab",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost362747\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">@Fictionarius: Contrary to what you think, it's pretty obvious <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dark Depths\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Depths\">Dark Depths</a> is the problematic one. That's why it is the one banned in Modern, not <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Vampire Hexmage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vampire Hexmage\">Vampire Hexmage</a>. A card like Dark Depths could either see no play at all or be a part of a broken combo, there is no middle ground. The Hexmage is a much more reasonable card; as if this even needs to be said.<br/><br/>As for infect, I think they made the mistake of not costing it as if it was double strike, because in decks that try to kill as fast as possible, it is basically double strike. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fencing Ace\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fencing Ace\">Fencing Ace</a> is a 1-power double strike that costs two. That's why <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Glistener Elf\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glistener Elf\">Glistener Elf</a> should not have costed one, and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Blighted Agent\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Blighted Agent\">Blighted Agent</a> probably should have been somewhat less powerful at two, if not gotten moved to three. 1/1 double strike for one is just not fair.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '362747'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy98788\">sweetgab</span>\r\n                                (2/9/2014 8:16:58 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
