    {
      "id": "PopularPost367934",
      "post_content": "Turn 1 combo:  \nStep 1: Play Mountain.  \nStep 2: Tap for [Goblin Guide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin Guide), [Lighning Serpent](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lighning Serpent), or [Spark Elemental](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spark Elemental).  \nStep 3: Discard a red card with cc 8 or more for Blazing Shoal.  \nStep 4: Attack.  \nStep 5: Discard 2 red cards for [Fury of the Horde](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fury of the Horde).  \nStep 6: Attack again.  \nStep 7: Win.  \n  \n7 cards = 20-22 damage on turn 1.  \nChances of this happening in an average game = not likely.",
      "posted_by": "BlakeHN",
